item.title: BlueYard in retrospect. Lisk founders first meeting. - Lisk Blog
item.description:
BlueYard in retrospect. Lisk founders first meeting. - Lisk Blog

Decentralized & Encrypted. That was the title of the first conference the Lisk founders ever attended. It was hosted by BlueYard in Berlin on June the 1st, 2016. Over 150 people participated in the discussion about Bitcoin, blockchain, decentralisation, and the future of the internet.
